record.title: DISMISSING ELECTION CONTEST RELATING TO OFFICE OF REPRESENTATIVE FROM FIFTH CONGRESSIONAL DISTRICT OF FLORIDA

speaking.paragraph: Mr. Speaker, I ask unanimous consent for the immediate consideration in the House of the resolution (H. Res. 463) dismissing the election contest relating to the office of Representative from the Fifth Congressional District of Florida.

record.narrative: The Clerk read the title of the resolution.
record.chair: Is there objection to the request of the gentleman from Pennsylvania?
record.narrative: The Clerk read the resolution, as follows:
